##Rarity

Castle notes (page 35), used or unused labels are extremely rare. 25 examples of the 1 piastre and 14 of the 2 piastre value were known to exist.
The 1 piastre included a vertical pair; of the 2, two are on covers.

These labels come on auction perhaps once every five-ten years. so grab one when you find them.

(The use of the labels at Larnaca is conjectural).

